# Finance Tracker Desktop App

A desktop application for personal finance tracking built with Java, Swing, JDBC, SQLite and Maven.

## Features

- Dashboard with financial summary
- Add, edit, delete and view incomes
- Add, edit, delete and view expenses
- Search incomes by description
- Search expenses by category
- Store data in SQLite database
- Generate monthly financial reports
- Expense statistics by category
- Export reports to CSV
- Calculate:
  - total income
  - card expenses
  - cash expenses
  - total expenses
  - monthly balance
  - cumulative balance

## Technologies

- Java
- Swing
- JDBC
- SQLite
- Maven

